Class IPAddressSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.aro.model.IPAddressSelection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class IPAddressSelection
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Contains methods for managing the settings applied to each IP address listed in the SelectApplications/IPs dialog.
